# The `SMDiagnostic` Class Reference

<DoxygenPage pluginConfig={pluginConfig}>

Instances of this class encapsulate one diagnostic report, allowing printing to a <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/raw-ostream">raw&#95;ostream</a> as a caret diagnostic. <a href="#details">More...</a>
